# ALL modules are tracked here — this umbrella monorepo is the source of truth
# (modules are NOT split into separate repos; see CLAUDE.md "module distribution").
# New modules under modules/ track automatically; only build/runtime junk is
# ignored (node_modules, __pycache__, *.pyc, data/, *.db above). The old
# allowlist silently dropped any module not on it (calendar/gog/steam) — gone.